*Duga* je bila dugačka. (The rainbow was long.)
Dugo smo čekali na *dugu*. (We waited a long time for the rainbow.)
Bila je *duga* dugačka poput mosta. (It was as long as a bridge.)
Pogledali smo *dugu* nad rekom. (We saw the rainbow over the river.)
Slikali smo *dugu* na nebu. (We took a picture of the rainbow in the sky.)